column2: A duffel bag full of guns was found under a bridge. Wild!

column10: I am pop legend Rod Stewart, why are you asking me about a duffel bag full of guns?
I made a song called Duffel Bag Boy in 2007, but that has nothing to do with the crime at hand

column2: I remember this feeling, from when I was that age and from when I was in fifth grade, but nothing really happened. I just experienced the period of dreaming about what might happen, when I was at that age. I feel like the movie could really be something that was envisioned by one of these characters.

column10: Allen currently lives with his wife in Whitefish, Montana.
I'll be ready for it to happen and that way it won't happen. It's a burden, being able to control situations with my hyper-vigilance, but it's my lot in life.
